    <centralBlocks>
      <Value><![CDATA[[
  {
    "key": "2bef6427-bec9-4094-82e3-b7cf631f68ff",
    "name": "Year One",
    "ncContentTypeAlias": "centralBlocks",
    "title": "Year One",
    "content": "<p>Not available in 2023.</p>"
  },
  {
    "key": "16a03122-244f-4f53-a3ae-386ca24283f4",
    "name": "Year Two",
    "ncContentTypeAlias": "centralBlocks",
    "title": "Year Two",
    "content": "<p>You will: </p>\n<ul>\n<li>Focus on management skills, in theory and the real world.</li>\n<li>Prepare for a challenging and rewarding 20-week internship in the UK or overseas.</li>\n<li>Have the opportunity (subject to availability) to study for one semester at a university overseas. For more information, visit <a href=\"/{localLink:umb://document/61c8e09441eb44ae940a55266617ab37}\" title=\"Exchanges and Study Abroad\">Exchanges and Study Abroad</a>*.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Modules</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Operations Management</li>\n<li>IHTM Internship</li>\n<li>Market Diversification in Hospitality and Tourism</li>\n<li>Human Resources Management</li>\n<li>Digital Business and eCommerce Futures</li>\n<li>Revenue Management in Hospitality and Tourism</li>\n</ul>\n<p>*This opportunity is available in both Years Two and Three however you will only be able to undertake it in one of those years. </p>"
  },
  {
    "key": "a28c6462-f9b1-4c40-8bf4-9eb492152484",
    "name": "Year Three",
    "ncContentTypeAlias": "centralBlocks",
    "title": "Year Three",
    "content": "<p>Not available for September 2023 entry.</p>"
  },
  {
    "key": "efe67a37-9776-48c9-93f2-4644a90a61fd",
    "name": "Year Four",
    "ncContentTypeAlias": "centralBlocks",
    "title": "Year Four",
    "content": "<p>You will:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Look at wider strategic issues such as 'What are the biggest challenges that hospitality and tourism managers face today?' or  'How do you successfully lead people in a highly competitive sector?' </li>\n<li>Learn to understand wider strategic issues and will develop your ideas into a dissertation in an area that you are passionate about.</li>\n<li>Have the flexibility and support required in your final year at QMU to progress to the next stages of your career, be that hospitality, tourism or academia.</li>\n<li>Engage with the significant contemporary issues of sustainability and social justice within hospitality and tourism.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Modules</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Strategy and Practice</li>\n<li>Dissertation</li>\n<li>International Destination Management and Marketing</li>\n<li>International Leadership for Hospitality and Tourism</li>\n<li>Contemporary Issues in Hospitality and Tourism</li>\n</ul>"
  },
  {
    "key": "c027a584-17e1-4517-90f9-456c9b29733b",
    "name": "Teaching, learning and assessment",
    "ncContentTypeAlias": "centralBlocks",
    "title": "Teaching, learning and assessment",
    "content": "<p>You will be taught in lectures, seminars and practical workshops. Outside these timetabled sessions you will be expected to continue learning through self-study. You will be assessed by a variety of methods during each semester.</p>"
  },
  {
    "key": "a3575620-7406-44df-a0d0-d08aef0d12d7",
    "name": "Placement/Internship",
    "ncContentTypeAlias": "centralBlocks",
    "title": "Placement/Internship",
    "content": "<p>You will complete a paid 20-week internship in Year Two, in the UK or overseas.</p>\n<p>Our tutors will help you prepare for this invaluable real-world experience and we will set up interviews on campus to make finding the perfect host organisation as straightforward as possible.</p>\n<p>Several bursaries are available to help with costs.</p>"
  },
  {
    "key": "dc157faf-f23b-4b9c-9216-9ecb65ec035b",
    "name": "Exchange opportunities",
    "ncContentTypeAlias": "centralBlocks",
    "title": "Exchange opportunities",
    "content": "<p>Yes</p>"
  },
  {
    "key": "57116f3b-ce08-4a0c-8873-3f0e26f5c69a",
    "name": "Entry requirements",
    "ncContentTypeAlias": "centralBlocks",
    "title": "Entry requirements",
    "content": "<p>Required subjects: Maths and English at Nat 5/GCSE level are preferred</p>\n<p>Entry onto Year One is not available. </p>\n<p>Direct Entry:</p>\n<p><em>Year Two</em></p>\n<ul>\n<li>HNC: HNC in a related subject with B in the graded unit</li>\n<li>Scottish Higher: BC at Advanced Higher in relevant subjects plus BB at Higher</li>\n<li>A Level: BBB in relevant subject</li>\n</ul>\n<p><em>Year Three</em></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Not available for this course. Please visit <a href=\"/{localLink:umb://document/4d45417d2bf74919ac97e6f7c51b5b9a}\" title=\"BA/BA (Hons) International Hospitality, Tourism and Events Management\">BA/BA (Hons) International Hospitality, Tourism and Events Management</a> for Year Three direct entry.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>For details of related HNC and HND courses, visit our<span> </span><a href=\"/study-here/access-to-higher-education/college-leavers-and-mature-students/\" title=\"College Leavers and Mature Students Advice\">College Leavers and Mature Students Advice page</a><span>. </span> </p>\n<p>Am I a <strong>Widening Access</strong> student?: We apply the minimum entry criteria to applicants who meet one or more contextual factor. To see if this would apply to you, please refer to the <a href=\"/study-here/access-to-higher-education/application-and-access/\">access and application</a> page.</p>"
  },
  {
    "key": "9f683135-7e57-4868-844a-1b53a5adc5b9",
    "name": "Careers",
    "ncContentTypeAlias": "centralBlocks",
    "title": "Careers",
    "content": "<p>Whether you want to work for a major global hotel brand in Dubai, manage the success of a tourism business in Scotland or launch a start-up that will change the way the industry works. This course will give you the competence and confidence to take the challenge on and shape the future of hospitality and tourism.</p>"
  },
  {
    "key": "37b4a8e6-38a6-4ab4-acfc-95c63299458e",
    "name": "Teaching staff, class sizes and timetables",
    "ncContentTypeAlias": "centralBlocks",
    "title": "Teaching staff, class sizes and timetables",
    "content": "<p>For more information, please visit ‘<a href=\"/{localLink:umb://document/363407ed108f454784361ca7c9d57713}\" title=\"How we teach and how you'll learn - Undergraduate\">How we teach and how you’ll learn</a>’.</p>"
  },
  {
    "key": "2bad1433-0b71-4b87-b96b-73b10d5e9d58",
    "name": "Awarding body",
    "ncContentTypeAlias": "centralBlocks",
    "title": "Awarding body",
    "content": "<p>QMU. More information is in the ‘External Review’ section of the <a href=\"/{localLink:umb://document/363407ed108f454784361ca7c9d57713}\" title=\"How we teach and how you'll learn - Undergraduate\">How we teach and how you'll learn page</a>.</p>"
  },
  {
    "key": "1c3f9c3d-0765-497a-be8d-8bb5b7c6262b",
    "name": "Open Day presentation",
    "ncContentTypeAlias": "centralBlocks",
    "title": "Open Day presentation",
    "content": "<div class=\"mceNonEditable embeditem\" data-embed-url=\"https://youtu.be/t7P3reGc9E4\" data-embed-height=\"346\" data-embed-width=\"721\" data-embed-constrain=\"true\"><iframe width=\"524\" height=\"295\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/t7P3reGc9E4?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" allowfullscreen=\"\" title=\"IHTM BA Hons\"></iframe></div>"
  }
]]]></Value>
